OL,3,CUS fury at chief scientist's 'dig' at
OL,4,CGeorge Bush's 'war on terror'
OL,6,FBritain's chief scientist sparked
OL,7,Foutrage in the United States after he
OL,8,Fwarned that climate change represented
OL,9,Fa greater global threat than
OL,10,Finternational terrorism, according to
OL,11,Fnewly-released government papers.
OL,13,FFiles released to the National
OL,14,FArchives at Kew, west London, show
OL,15,Fofficials feared Professor Sir David
OL,16,FKing's remarks would be seen as a
OL,17,F"dig" at President George Bush's "war
OL,18,Fon terror" in the wake of the 9/11
OL,19,Fattacks on New York.
