OL,6,FPrime minister Tony Blair was warned
OL,7,Fthat Sir David risked being branded an
OL,8,F"extremist" in Washington, potentially
OL,9,Fundermining British efforts to get the
OL,10,FAmericans to address the issue of
OL,11,Fglobal warming, which was rising up
OL,12,Fthe political agenda.
OL,14,FSir David made his comments in an
OL,15,Farticle for the US journal, Science,
OL,16,Fpublished in January 2004 ` less than
OL,17,Fthree years after the al Qaida attack
OL,18,Fwhich destroyed the Twin Towers and
OL,19,Fwhich remained fresh in American
OL,20,Fmemories.
