OL,3,CUS fury at chief scientist's 'dig' at
OL,4,CGeorge Bush's 'war on terror'
OL,6,F"He said that the article, and
OL,7,Fparticularly the comparison between
OL,8,Fthe dangers posed by climate change
OL,9,Fand terrorism, was proving deeply
OL,10,Funhelpful here," Mr Brenton wrote.
OL,12,F"Within the administration, he was
OL,13,Fhaving to deal with questions about
OL,14,Fwhy they were working in co-operation
OL,15,Fwith the UK on this subject. And there
OL,16,Fwere also already hints of political
OL,17,Frepercussions on the Hill.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@PO]tD@AOU
