OL,6,FIn London, Vicki Bakhshi, a senior No
OL,7,F10 adviser, warned Mr Blair that Sir
OL,8,FDavid's comments "will be taken in the
OL,9,FUS as a dig at the war on terror".
OL,11,F"Together with the blunt criticism on
OL,12,Fthe US policy stance, this is likely
OL,13,Fto mark Sir David in the eyes of the
OL,14,Fadministration as something of an
OL,15,Fextremist," she wrote.
OL,17,F"This could undermine the
OL,18,Feffectiveness of his efforts on
OL,19,Fclimate change in future."
